{"title":"【084】CSS布局之溢出处理","slug":"hell0-world30","date":"2022-10-21T05:02:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:21:05.024Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world30.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                types        <br><br>                    overflow                          内容太大","covers":["./by3.jpg"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>types</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"types-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <br><br>\n    <!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>overflow</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./overflow-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"overflowTest\">\n        <p>\n          内容太大<span id=\"more\"></span>,无法容纳在指定区域时,是否要裁剪内容或在必要时添加滚动条。使用overflow属性。\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          visible:默认。溢出内容没有被剪掉;\n          hidden:溢出内容被剪切;\n        </p>\n        <p>\n        <img src=\"./by3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width:600px;>\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          scroll:溢出内容被剪掉了;\n          auto:类似于scroll;  \n          如果只希望一个方向右滚动条可使用overflow-x/y,指定的是水平方向还是垂直方向。\n          有时，文字标题或文字内容所在的容器空间有限，不能出现全部内容时，会出现一个省略号\n          示意读者，内容不全可点击显示全部内容的实现：\n        </p>\n    </div> \n    <h1 id=\"a\">点击请欣赏风花博客</h1>  \n    <h1 id=\"b\">点击请欣赏风花博客</h1> \n    <br><br><br>\t\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}